    @"Juniper is an .NET 7 and TypeScript framework for building WebXR applications. It is an evolution of my previous project, Primrose."),
    ("Calla", "Calla", "Spatialized audio chat", "https://github.com/capnmidnight/Calla", "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/capnmidnight/Calla/master/repo-preview.jpg",
